================================================================================

This software represents a comprehensive creative automation platform
for ComfyUI integration through the Model Context Protocol (MCP).

Version 1.0.0 includes:

- 89 specialized tools for image and video generation
- Workflow automation and preset management
- Intelligent prompt optimization with AI
- Batch operations with dependency management
- Real-time preview and progress monitoring
- LoRA model management integration
- Advanced masking and control features

All code in this repository has been written specifically for this project
with the goal of providing a comprehensive creative automation platform.